267
00:29:44,354 --> 00:29:46,070
Ini milikku, kembalikan!

268
00:29:46,154 --> 00:29:47,972
Tidak, kupukul kau nanti.

269
00:29:48,824 --> 00:29:51,983
[ Menghina logat]
